<div id="welcome-message">
  <h3>Welcome To</h3>
  <h1>Free at Noon</h1>
  <p>We’re a small group of people at Penn who want to take advantage of our random pockets of free time — to meet new people and to keep up with friends.</p>
  <p>It’s a pain to schedule that stuff though. This tool takes the hassle out of seeing if anyone is free when you are. Join us!</p>
  <%= link_to "Join the Group", "#", id: "join-group-button", class: "btn" %>
</div>

<div id="user-info-form">
  <h2>Woohoo! Welcome.</h2>

<%= form_for(resource, as: resource_name, url: registration_path(resource_name)) do |f| %>
  <%= devise_error_messages! %>

  <div><%= f.label :first_name, id: "user-info-form-label" %><br />
    <%= f.text_field :first_name, autofocus: true, type: "text", placeholder: "Jon" %></div>

  <div><%= f.label :last_name, id: "user-info-form-label" %><br />
    <%= f.text_field :last_name, type: "text", placeholder: "Huntsman" %></div>

  <div><%= f.label :phone_number, id: "user-info-form-label" %><br />
    <%= f.text_field :phone_number, type: "tel", placeholder: "650-291-3866" %></div>

  <div><%= f.label :email, id: "user-info-form-label" %><br />
    <%= f.email_field :email, type: "email", placeholder: "jon.huntsman97@aol.net" %></div>

  <div><%= f.label :password, id: "user-info-form-label" %><br />
    <%= f.password_field :password, type: "password", autocomplete: "off", placeholder: "*********" %></div>

  <%= link_to "Continue", "#", id: "continue-button", class: "btn" %>
<% end %>
</div>

<div id="additional-user-info-form">
<%= form_for "user" do |f| %>
  <h2> Just a bit more. </h2>
  <div><%= f.label :year, id: "user-info-form-label" %><br />
    <%= f.text_field :year, type: "number", placeholder: "2015" %></div>

  <div><%= f.label :team, id: "user-info-form-label" %><br />
    <%= f.text_field :team, placeholder: "Editorial" %></div>

  <div><%= f.label :fun_fact, id: "user-info-form-label" %><br />
    <%= f.text_field :fun_fact, placeholder: "I love watching birds." %></div>
  <%= link_to "Done", "#", id: "done-button", class:"btn"%>
<% end %>
</div>

<div id="thankyou-message">
  <h2>You're a champion!</h2>
  <p>You did it! Welcome to the gang. What happens next you ask?</p>
  <p>It's simple. On days that you're free you'll get a text at 9:00AM (so you can respond when you wake up) asking if you are up for coffee/lunch with another member. If you say yes and the system sees a match, it'll put you in a groupme with your lunchmate and you two can decide on the place. That's it!</p>
  <p>Feel free to hit us up (650-291-3866 / freeatnoon@gmail.com) if you wanna chat about something, wanna set up a private Free At Noon circle for a club, or have any other thoughts. Looking forward to seeing you!</p>
  <p>Oh, and make sure to check out <a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dQw4w9WgXcQ">these etiquette guidelines</a> before your first meeting.</p>
</br>
</div>
